View\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>여러분..&nbsp;<br></span><span>문학진원장님의 진료 시간 변경안내 알려드리려구요~<br></span><span><br></span><span><br></span><span>문학진원장님이&nbsp;9월부터&nbsp;<br></span><span>경희대학교&nbsp;대학원&nbsp;동서의학과에&nbsp;강사(외래교수)로&nbsp;발령받았습니다.&nbsp;<br></span><span><br></span><span>그에&nbsp;따라&nbsp;강의&nbsp;일정으로&nbsp;인해&nbsp;<br></span><span>부득이하게&nbsp;수요일&nbsp;진료를&nbsp;못하게&nbsp;되었습니다.&nbsp; <br> <br>9월19일 수요일부터&nbsp;매주&nbsp;수요일은&nbsp;문학진원장님은&nbsp;휴진합니다.<br></span><span><br></span><span>&nbsp; <br>앞으로 수요일 내원 하시는 환자분들께서는 <br></span><span>나효석원장님께&nbsp;진료받으시면 됩니다 ^^<br></span><span><br></span><span></span><span></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"se_component se_image default\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-justify\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\" >\n        <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"imgId\" : \"SEDOC-1537264267961--1377295459_image_0_img\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dd221106c55ca0e8.jpg\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                            <img id=\"SEDOC-1537264267961--1377295459_image_0_img\" class=\"se_mediaImage __se_img_el\" src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dd221106c55ca0e8.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/dd221106c55ca0e8.jpg\" data-width=\"960\" data-height=\"960\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" data-attachment-id=\"I30JYlspufe8Av9eZGJJz9T_7rZU\" alt=\"\">\n        \n        </a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                    <div class=\"se_textView\">\n                        <p class=\"se_textarea\"><!-- SE3-TEXT { --><span>문학진원장님께서 이제 수요일에 한의원에 안나오시는건&nbsp;<br></span><span>아쉽지만 ㅠㅠ<br></span><span><br></span><span>그래도 경희대학교 대학원 강사로 발령받으신 일은<br></span><span>축하 해드릴일이니까<br></span><span><br></span><span>우리모두 해피해피~<br></span><span><br></span><span></span><!-- } SE3-TEXT --></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_sticker default \">\n\t<div class=\"se_sectionArea se_align-left\">\n\t\t<div class=\"se_editArea\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"se_viewArea\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"SEDOC-1537264267961--1377295459_sticker_0\" class=\"se_sticker_area\">\n\t\t\t\t \t<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"se_mediaArea __se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7c5f1453eeae2295.png\", \"packCode\" : \"line_choco\", \"seq\" : \"11\", \"width\" : \"160\", \"height\" : \"160\"}'>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7c5f1453eeae2295.png\" class=\"__se_img_el\" alt=\"스티커 이미지\" width=\"160\" height=\"160\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"se_component se_paragraph default\">\n    <div class=\"se_sectionArea\">\n        <div class=\"se_editArea\">\n            <div class=\"se_viewArea se_ff_nanumgothic se_fs_T3 se_align-left\" >\n                <div class=\"se_editView\">\n                   